{"tid":1895567,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國呼籲中國人切勿到美國旅遊","createTime":"2020-02-24T15:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-24T15:23:49.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c778965a75286f56feccba751abc5b7d1c172a47","tid":1895567,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:22:41.000Z","msg":"國家文化和旅遊部指，中國遊客在美國受到不公平對待，呼籲遊客切勿前往當地。<br />\n<br />\n文化和旅遊部在官方網頁發公告，指近期由於美方的過度防疫措施，以及美國國內安全形勢，中國遊客在美國屢次遭到不公平對待，提醒中國遊客切實提高安全防範意識，切勿前往美國旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n因應新型冠狀病毒疫情，美國上月底將中國的旅遊警告級別提升至最高，呼籲國民不要前往中國，又禁止十四天內到過中國的非美國公民入境。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部曾經指摘美方是反應過激過度，不斷製造和散播恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=381844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D381844&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwaGgm0NOSfkDZSs230CVm%2Fs%3D&h=f5d8c6df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D381844&h=a2c1df1f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=381844</a>"},{"pid":"4703c13399ee5ae8a25d897b13167981a605e4a8","tid":1895567,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"家下唔係你飛我，係我飛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}